  "answer": "class Node: def __init__(self, x, next=None, random=None): self.val=int(x); self.next=next; self.random=random\ndef copyRandomList(head):\n    if not head: return None\n    m = {None: None}; c = head\n    while c: m[c] = Node(c.val); c = c.next\n    c = head\n    while c: m[c].next = m[c.next]; m[c].random = m[c.random]; c = c.next\n    return m[head]",
